highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Canada. “Tears” is the highest at #2.
“Tears” by Sabrina Carpenter is the highest new entry on Top Songs Canada at #2.
“Sweater Weather” by The Neighbourhood has been on Top Songs Canada the longest, at 257 weeks straight.
“Feel Good Inc.” by Gorillaz and De La Soul is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Canada, up 71 spots at #94.
